OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,FA UK expert responsible for
OL,7,Fimplementing a Goods and Services Tax
OL,8,F(GST) in Jersey back in 2008 has
OL,9,Fwarned Guernsey that it must take
OL,10,Faction to address its precarious
OL,11,Ffinancial position.
OL,13,FSteve Lowthorpe helped introduce the
OL,14,Flevy in 10 countries and warns of the
OL,15,Frisk to Guernsey's economy if it does
OL,16,Fnot act soon.
