OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,FHe explains: "If they don't do
OL,7,Fanything and carry on operating with a
OL,8,Fdeficit, then it means a reduction in
OL,9,Fvital services. I don't think it's
OL,10,Ftenable."
OL,12,FGST introduction to Jersey
OL,14,FMr Lowthorpe played a key role in how
OL,15,Fa Value Added Tax (VAT) system was
OL,16,Fintroduced in Jersey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/14
