OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,FHe says: "I came over in 2005 because
OL,7,Fthe States put out a tender for an
OL,8,Forganisation to come and carry out a
OL,9,Ffeasibility study, so the organisation
OL,10,Fthat I was working for at the time,
OL,11,FThe Crown Agents, won the tender.
OL,13,F"I came with a team and did exactly
OL,14,Fwhat was requested, what is the
OL,15,Ffeasibility of implementing a VAT-type
OL,16,Fsystem in Jersey?
OL,18,F"That was the best part of six months.
OL,19,FWe were then contracted to implement
OL,20,Ffrom 2006.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
