OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1758219599
OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,F"We said, what do you want to happen
OL,7,Fwith the options? A UK-style VAT, or
OL,8,Fyou could have a simpler, broader-
OL,9,Fbased GST similar to New Zealand,
OL,10,FSingapore."
OL,12,FThe Government of Jersey introduced a
OL,13,F3% GST in 2008, which was later raised
OL,14,Fto 5% in 2011.
OL,16,FMr Lowthorpe says his work also saw
OL,17,Fhim travel to the other Bailiwick.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/14
