OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,FHe explains: "Part of my remit was to
OL,7,Fgo over to Guernsey, so they were well
OL,8,Faware in 2006 or 2007 what the plans
OL,9,Fwere and what we were going to do with
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,F"In 2016, when I retired, we were
OL,13,Fstill having conversations, meetings,
OL,14,Fand going over. It's a political
OL,15,Fdecision to implement any new tax
OL,16,Fsystem.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/14
