OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1758219599
OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,F"I'm not a salesman, I don't sell VAT,
OL,7,Fall I do is help as much as I can. If
OL,8,Fa government decides that it wishes to
OL,9,Fimplement it, then I will help based
OL,10,Fon the experiences I have had in the
OL,11,Fpast."
OL,13,FCould GST come to Guernsey?
OL,15,FWith Guernsey's financial deficit
OL,16,Fcontinuing to grow and infrastructure
OL,17,Fprojects put on hold, the previous
OL,18,FStates approved GST in late 2024,
OL,19,Fwhich could be introduced in 2027.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/14
