OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,FIn September this year, the Policy and
OL,7,FResources Committee published a
OL,8,Ftimeline, listing how a sub-committee
OL,9,Fwill look at tax reform choices.
OL,11,FA final debate over whether to bring
OL,12,Fin GST-plus or another option is
OL,13,Fexpected in the first half of 2026.
OL,15,FA second workstream will run in tandem
OL,16,Fwith the review, continuing
OL,17,Fpreparations for a GST-plus package of
OL,18,FGST, income tax, and social security
OL,19,Freforms that was agreed by the
OL,20,Fprevious Assembly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
