OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,FDeputy Gavin St. Pier, Vice-President
OL,7,Fof the Policy & Resources Committee
OL,8,F(P&R) and a member of the Tax Review
OL,9,FSub-committee, says: "There has been
OL,10,Fmuch discussion and multiple States'
OL,11,Fdebates over the last decade about how
OL,12,Fbest to solve the challenging state of
OL,13,Four public finances.
OL,15,F"The status quo is unsustainable. The
OL,16,Fprevious States agreed in November
OL,17,F2024 to carry out the necessary
OL,18,Fpreparatory work to implement what has
OL,19,Fbecome known as the GST-plus package
OL,20,Fof tax reforms.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
