OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1758219599
OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,F"This package includes a Goods and
OL,7,FServices Tax but also reforms to
OL,8,Fincome tax and social security that
OL,9,Fwould mitigate the impact of a GST,
OL,10,Fparticularly for the less well-off
OL,11,Fmembers of our community."
OL,13,FDeputy Charles Parkinson, a member of
OL,14,FP&R who will lead the Tax Review Sub-
OL,15,Fcommittee, adds: "While there
OL,16,Fcontinues to be healthy discussion and
OL,17,Fdebate around the right solution, what
OL,18,Fshould be beyond discussion at this
OL,19,Fstage is that there is an urgent need
OL,20,Ffor tax reform to safeguard public
OL,21,Ffinances in the years ahead.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
