OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,F"This cannot be an issue that
OL,7,Fcontinues to be kicked down the road."
OL,9,FGuernsey's resistance
OL,11,FMr Lowthorpe explains why Guernsey may
OL,12,Fhave resisted introducing GST.
OL,14,FHe says: "The biggest mistake was that
OL,15,Finitially, you will always get
OL,16,Fresistance to the thought of
OL,17,Fimplementing a new tax; it's not
OL,18,Freplacing anything, it's an additional
OL,19,Ftax burden, and the burden falls on
OL,20,Fthe public.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
