OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1758219599
OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,F"It's never an easy thing to do. The
OL,7,Fbig mistake was that whenever there
OL,8,Fwas negativity, and I read some of it,
OL,9,Fand it wasn't true, the movement grew,
OL,10,Fand I never saw politicians really
OL,11,Fcounter this negativity.
OL,13,F"In Jersey, when we did have some
OL,14,Fnegative feedback, it was answered. We
OL,15,Fwould always write to people if they
OL,16,Fhad written in, so we always tried to
OL,17,Fbe open and honest with the public,
OL,18,Fbut I haven't seen that same response
OL,19,Ffrom politicians in Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
