OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1758219599
OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,F"The members to me seem to be very
OL,7,Ffocused on the corporate tax side and
OL,8,Fless on GST. It has to be good news."
OL,10,FHowever, even if the additional tax is
OL,11,Fvoted through by politicians, Mr
OL,12,FLowthorpe believes it may be
OL,13,Fchallenging to get it up and running
OL,14,Ffor 2027.
OL,16,FHe explains: "It's ambitious because
OL,17,Fthere are rules that have been applied
OL,18,Felsewhere in the world, and I have
OL,19,Fbeen around in 10 countries where they
OL,20,Fhave imposed GST.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
