OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1758219599
OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,F"They just allow at least 12 months
OL,7,Fafter the enactment of legislation,
OL,8,Fregulations, and instructions for key
OL,9,Fpeople to know what the tax system is.
OL,11,F"We need a year or two to educate
OL,12,Ftaxpayers on the system."
OL,14,FEssentially, Mr Lowthorpe hasn't said
OL,15,Fanything that isn't already well known
OL,16,Fby Guernsey politicians, especially
OL,17,Fthose leading the charge to tax reform.
OL,19,FHowever, hearing these concerns voiced
OL,20,Fby Mr Lowthorpe just reinforces how
OL,21,Fcritical Guernsey's next steps are.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/14
