OL,3,CTax expert urges Guernsey to take
OL,4,Caction as GST debate rumbles on
OL,6,FLike most places, the island had a
OL,7,Fvisceral response to the idea that a
OL,8,FGST would be brought in at all.
OL,10,FThe difference was that the anti-GST
OL,11,Fmovement successfully crushed its
OL,12,Fintroduction in 2023 and despite
OL,13,Fpoliticians voting through a GST
OL,14,Fpackage last year, its implementation
OL,15,Fis far from a given.
OL,17,FIn fact, during the election campaign,
OL,18,Fhalf of the successful candidates said
OL,19,Fthey oppose it, and there are plenty
OL,20,Fof chances to derail its arrival.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/14
